message: Hello! Thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
I can't believe the terrible service I've received from your company! I am extremely angry and frustrated!
I'm truly sorry to hear that you're feeling this way. I want to help. Before we proceed, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Thank you for confirming. Could you also provide me with your date of birth, please?
Great, thank you. To continue, could you confirm the first line of your address and postcode?
Thank you for completing security. I appreciate your cooperation. How may I assist you further today?
My policy was cancelled without my authorization, and I have not received any explanation or refund. This is unacceptable!
I understand the seriousness of the situation. Let me look into this for you. A possible resolution could be to review the cancellation and process a refund if necessary. Does this work for you?
That's not good enough! I demand to speak to a manager right now!
I completely understand your frustration. Let me see if I can escalate this for you. Please allow me a moment to find a suitable solution.
You better make sure this gets sorted quickly. I won't accept anything less!
I value your feedback and I'm here to help. I will do my best to ensure this matter is resolved promptly. Thank you for your patience.
I'm glad that I was able to help. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
